{
  "stem": "15197.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was how I escaped getting out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would like to tell you how I escaped smuggling into the ghetto dynamite.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was a different time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was on the point, the smuggling point, of [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And over there, a group of Polish smugglers smuggled in food into the ghetto and of course, Poles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was their way of making a living for some smugglers, a very dangerous one because the ghetto wall was always patrolled by German, by Polish police.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But in this particular place, it was the Jewish police and the Polish police was bribed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was a ladder put at the wall of one side, on the Polish side, of the ghetto wall.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was at that time already told by phone to my group, [INAUDIBLE], where I am going to smuggle in.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And these were packages of five kilo dynamite put in greasy paper to look like I am smuggling butter.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Usually, the smugglers paid a certain amount of money to the foreman and he was staying near the ladder.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they gave him the money, went up the ladder on the other side, and jumped on the other side of the wall into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the smuggle was going on and that was mine next and I gave also the money to the foreman and I went up with my package.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was not suspicious for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And while I was on top of the wall, shooting started.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was on top and shooting started to come closer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The foreman snatched away the ladder and I was not able not to go back to the Polish side and I didn't see anybody on the Jewish side.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
